{{Top|leg}}
A '''stun pistol''' was a type of [[Stun blaster/Legends|stun blaster]].<ref name="Young Jedi Knights: Shadow Academy">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Shadow Academy]]''</ref>

Designed exclusively for nonlethal crowd control, stun-pistols only fired [[Stun/Legends|stun]] bolts, and emitted a glowing blue arc that could immobilize an organic target, but caused no damage to inanimate objects.

Since they were designed for stunning only, they had a longer range than most blaster's stun settings, with a typical stun pistol getting fifty shots out of a single [[Power cell/Legends|power pack]].<ref name="The Unknown Regions">''[[The Unknown Regions]]''</ref> Additionally, the bolts were heavy enough that they could pierce medium armors like [[Stormtrooper armor/Legends|stormtrooper armor]].<ref name="Young Jedi Knights: Shadow Academy">''[[Young Jedi Knights: Shadow Academy]]''</ref>

